Move stride programming to dpu_hw_sspp_setup_sourceaddress(), so that
dpu_hw_sspp_setup_rects() programs only source and destination
rectangles.

Signed-off-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@linaro.org>
